        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Heat</strong> 1-2 tbsp olive oil in a pan over a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>When</strong> hot, add the carrot, onion and garlic and cook for 3-4 min until the vegetables are soft but not coloured</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
