    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> the mince and tomato paste to the pan and give everything a good stir</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bring</strong> the pan to a boil and season generously with salt and pepper</p>\r\n<p><strong>Set</strong> aside until your mash is ready&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 5,
