            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, shred the spring greens discarding the woody stems</p>\r\n<p>Tip: Roll the leaves before shredding them to make it quick and easy</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> approx. 2cm of water to a large pan with a lid on a high heat, bring to a boil and add the spring greens&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cook</strong> for 6 min or until tender, then drain</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
